    <div class="main review-item" id="4919765">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4919765/" class="title-link">秦汉史读书笔记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4919765"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1192533/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1192533-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1192533/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">大战朱仙镇</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-04-23"
      class="main-meta">2011-04-23 23:47:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4919765_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是适合普通读者的通史性质的书，介绍由列国时代到一统的秦、前、后汉（中国习惯称西汉、东汉）的政治、经济、文化的发展、变化、对后世的影响。 这学期修“汉唐史”，照理，我应当将时间花在针对各项专题的研究著作上做更深层次的阅读或直接读《汉书》或《后汉书》，可是有份...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">19有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
